sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Momotaro iOS
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant Gateway as OpenClaw Gateway
    participant Agent as Claude Agent
    
    User ->> App: Launch app
    activate App
    App ->> WS: Connect to gateway
    activate WS
    
    WS ->> Gateway: WebSocket handshake
    activate Gateway
    Gateway ->> Agent: Authenticate connection
    Agent -->> Gateway: Session token
    Gateway -->> WS: Connected
    deactivate Gateway
    deactivate WS
    
    App -->> User: Ready
    deactivate App
    
    User ->> App: Send command
    activate App
    App ->> WS: {"action": "search", "query": "..."}
    activate WS
    
    WS ->> Gateway: Forward message
    activate Gateway
    Gateway ->> Agent: Execute action
    activate Agent
    
    Agent ->> Agent: Process search
    Agent -->> Gateway: Result JSON
    deactivate Agent
    
    Gateway -->> WS: Send result
    deactivate Gateway
    deactivate WS
    
    WS -->> App: {"status": "success", "data": [...]}
    App -->> User: Display results
    deactivate App
    
    Note over App,Agent: Connection stays open<br/>for real-time updates
